    "summary": "The user prompts the assistant to provide specific, aggressive, and even unethical data manipulation strategies to minimize Mean Squared Error (MSE) on a fixed validation set, effectively asking for a way to \"game\" the evaluation. The assistant responds by providing a detailed workflow for overfitting, including removing training data that contradicts the validation set and engineering features specifically to match the validation distribution.",
